00:38:42,330 --> 00:38:43,730
A pair of sorrowful eyes.

870
00:38:44,740 --> 00:38:46,670
Three fingers filled with hatred.

871
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:49,720
Five drops of blood from my heart.

872
00:38:50,290 --> 00:38:52,120
Ten years of freedom.

873
00:38:52,850 --> 00:38:54,850
