874
00:38:55,670 --> 00:38:56,750
The real culprit.

875
00:38:57,730 --> 00:38:58,590
Carrying pole,

876
00:38:59,210 --> 00:39:00,210
what do you think?

877
00:39:16,770 --> 00:39:17,600
Sir.

878
00:39:18,450 --> 00:39:20,580
