890
00:40:29,660 --> 00:40:31,000
And then I would rightfully

891
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:32,490
become the master of the Yanmen Sect.

892
00:40:32,490 --> 00:40:33,230
This wonderful

893
00:40:33,230 --> 00:40:34,960
