00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:50,970
Today,

903
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,770
you're doomed to die.

904
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,240
Mr. Tang,

905
00:41:11,250 --> 00:41:12,650
I want to find Chuanxiang

906
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:14,480
and ask him

907
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,690
why he wanted to kill me.

908
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:22,920
We used to be best friends
who would die for each other.

909
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,720
