912
00:41:36,810 --> 00:41:38,280
does that make it my karma?

913
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:52,450
Tang Lici, do you see now?

914
00:41:55,710 --> 00:41:57,550
Such a tiny pill

915
00:41:57,910 --> 00:41:59,480
can turn the best friends

916
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,640
into bitter enemies

917
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:03,440
and make family members
betray and kill each other.

918
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:05,480
Who can resist the temptation

919
00:42:05,530 --> 00:42:06,960
of overnight wealth, glory,

920
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,880
and unparalleled martial arts?

921
00:42:09,290 --> 00:42:10,030
I have already spread it

922
00:42:10,030 --> 00:42:11,800
throughout the martial arts world.

923
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:13,280
It has returned to this world

924
00:42:13,280 --> 00:42:14,550
all because of you,

925
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,070
Tang Lici.

926
00:42:16,290 --> 00:42:16,960
This time,

927
00:42:17,620 --> 00:42:19,620
I'll make you wish you were dead.

928
